caption&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 24px; font-size: 16px;"&gt;角落里坐着极端主义者，他们认为伊朗永远不应该能够浓缩任何铀，因为核燃料生产本质上是双重用途的。该技术可用于发电和制造炸弹。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 24px; font-size: 16px;"&gt;美国总统唐纳德·特朗普政府中的极端主义者&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/a/sc/BHMn-8tibNHDHOEhbwn0KJnLEITxFhCiAJErsxljvBNquOsqQo1gO40wAdWciI7Dtb6ciOvR_tdUtfKe19hgqi_L3FK-pyOnc5VmhtO9uoPdSa4h6mihfVnfYGBN6gaBVAFwrhT4VNNX0oxJAfS-BIwtU_oQxFpAw04HbQFGkaYkjiohTV5-5WTm-vIQPbhtjpkdvp3fOQ1mcoSkDzgZOKKHpM-OzEAYEicUKW-YnZF2K2cCa8kRlh0phfUIR0nVjJ-QPxse1Eqb4K5sS76tBwosLl4BEsB7Pzm5j-qyurwagCdFbxS6tXhkLOrqyJyhEY97_bQnc7K73R8QWYijUH3eMb4JV3fQUiNJV43EBYcHVZKrcQpiPKjbfmTppInIXCgx4biKXDdCLn95PSNEaLA6DMiVyNbpnBZuhO4vPCS5q_d4qB7R7EIDEUMMhFBWkXjEBsvY5oxh2cbQfKzs2i7W9MYSKkdpCS3vrbtTpTZ5Zklw6kz3XHhbHr6cD_TFD2KYInm-6xoeQlNTjk3YYHtOv2bgxP-CcqB_-JvI1P8/3arDjcWlPtcYMNFPcBTpNIv0ITy7jNYg/21" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="font-size: inherit; color: #00e;" target="_blank" title="为什么释放伊朗资产是特朗普的政治难题"&gt;提倡制裁&lt;/a&gt;和军事力量来强制遵守这一政策。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 24px; font-size: 16px;"&gt;还有实用主义者，他们建议伊朗可以在一定限度内并在严格的国际监督下进行铀浓缩活动。他们认为，这位 80 岁的科技精灵已经摆脱了酒瓶，建立一个国际问责体系比永久战争&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/a/sc/jKDcY6xu-DKE2xGGW1BNl_ZzL37jtmHs-W_wg6TBeHyquJkQT7uVd1L9zJlTYPAiodcVegFcsV8ctW8I-2ZjhXFrP3olK-5mODeNc9g-Z83koesxs_WPsDWL5QbF-6cuBKrGuTz-52FamQf3x3GK6irL3SzV3RgMcfvAgsXdGLOIv68nEb8zt4xtfmeturXomKzcy_lhguU0Ck38iUMwkDbXkM1vymZ7D5GLa32d26jAanrC4Lp5_zglgzBHtARIFAA3XNUgugcQ-Z-gH8_DSw_a41S_Avhvbc3iXP8RF-jeWO_t1CsLQE-V_D2R5RM6gBk8EaFmtHGhYEmcGM1HJsN0dzi1G8dJ9kebcIYAMbPQXrU6wuB4G5ASvTY4JsuJWprTikmEU-9SreKR_VFRuFwVavlfzDbn7xvK8EbiNyxkkfrfOm0VzrEFQA3hqx1KJ_lGBE57k1MAnwMnv5ZVpHMO20J6TbqaA0S5J-SksGDKcSdZHtu6xA45y2ur3NlzFaCh0vpew0jyTJZx8Kn-MBAdNontpYh5NdD4PX2in5qBVviakO5ygQ/Ad-R2iX5U-kBWDNkxkY-eCFTLVydyXLs/21" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="font-size: inherit; color: #00e;" target="_blank" title="混乱的伊朗谈判让特朗普声称胜利，但尚未实现和平"&gt;更好&lt;/a&gt;。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 24px; font-size: 16px;"&gt;美国前总统巴拉克·奥巴马 (Barack Obama) 2015 年达成的协议旨在尽早发现伊朗的任何欺诈行为。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 24px; font-size: 16px;"&gt;随着特朗普&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/a/sc/2286758oSG1PJcHljxting7Brr0NpAp6ovKeYDxWhHaduOiW663Dp9EwmNx8qjJsI-KI1xFynJz6eUCKYtKHugdSi_Oc7-y5MJjN6RhL9hoGkutQ1VcguurSQb_BuMTrxepdezdbPJvvHlD1sbXdePgKbOMEWvXCZahDyMzmHEKOH4WsVij3yd1PD-eeCV3fDyzHXIpBU1ifFOmxkn0poIi_kUfadLDs5tLMOtHcothPYVdZ6V5UC4AYsGnp29af2BASz48drOUrivVoU9ZqywQ6kYemlnOugeouoSWItXrK9PEpJQVk2_-1Qx9qi0t-_DZCtUaUw4G-xw68xVThw4O92HHap8PgZVKVo0gt62jloM7VHoYUSod6cuU1Cccma64D7AcW8IIO1O9mgC4vLtN-Cn9nXlMWsVCikqF5aAWcyOWPlbvzSdt14QbM6qBaO7RNV-qe7lojpNJZ-EJJbf7PildLpz_hklJkn8zT7jBQp4GeQML6pEe4RDP1ysBudEQYn_fSwI7dIKrNUWa9u7jBLHBPNCmV2HJiKQ/zkvnLxgW5eyEM2GHJyi28EN8Aforrwug/21" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="font-size: inherit; color: #00e;" target="_blank" title="阅读美国和伊朗之间的 14 点备忘录草案"&gt;现在认识&lt;/a&gt;到伊朗不是一颗可以轻易敲打的钉子，他面临着打造一个比他在第一个任期内于 2018 年拆除的捕鼠器更好的捕鼠器的&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/a/sc/MPtiSropQvx0yyD9uhO6ox7ylzxXoM1wEapivKOxI6EwUQjCihxaTenpnoDYhR_p9xdV7sbdCKTLINdpJLayt0IZWhiORhkkLMdnXUHhtkiY_-NIPdTKvnbdV04sFx56jKytdBiixL-y7zac4Wg7HCjjzcyf7YsuR4GlNGAj5jEtNhKSs1Mi9u-4tGdmUb3OSkQyzQu4SoQCDpKaxOaJrE7se7NSkYXO3H_ik68MqFV5abl_skbEuZ2gaukqnslyIzEXv2_TwvAheMEiKB0q-VlP9g-0IoB_SfxMblzNH7GkcXLz01kDs4P4BbwHGi_3Fg4JmX2hfE5Cwm2NIf_MbS-05grzUQWyd8Ly4QEPvSXK8VBtI_JrASWeZAVzVPP0gSfCPkxb2qpOPo6vEEo_Ow7mVxrHvC-FtrHhk3owp_5gVaIIpfmY-vkr-m7PQQjW4wh9JyTH-EMjv6hzRNxpFjT_6Qqv4Rx2NmHfilXLkOw/yFeOKTLr_brEM57ZOJXRwKhzjVkhz4rx/21" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="font-size: inherit; color: #00e;" target="_blank" title="寻找伊朗隐藏铀矿的选择：攻击、谈判或等待"&gt;挑战&lt;/a&gt;。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 24px; font-size: 16px;"&gt;过去25年收集的数据显示，西方国家等待&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/a/sc/YjcpvOvbrPzV_Mm5IMmMhPOI28gQZKqsnezl6AacRLEA2lbsT-WMtIH_NqkB4JEPDt53tMIGCupXohgmfM0_Z9QNBpIIf4QcE1svr2E9PCerQT23DBbx0OmcePkKe4qQ8tQvOp8sZ6Glt105ksih8H_LMwYxnHjUZ34T3722SUYt186097UByTXiX0jsxu8t5NKoqLAxm0zXsO4D